<content>
        
    
Aug 5 (Reuters) - Steve Wuori, president of Enbridge Inc's
(ENB.TO) liquids pipeline division, at a news conference in
Marshall, Michigan, on the company's oil pipeline rupture and
spill:

 * Says may be able to cut out damaged Mich. pipe section
late Friday * Says still working with authorities on schedule for
pipeline restart
 (Reporting by Jeffrey Jones)




